name: Rico Tubbs from Miami Vice - Phillip Michael Thomas
description:
The character Rico Tubbs from Miami Vice as portrayed by Philip Michael Thomas.
Made using stills from the series and promotional images.

Training Details:
15 images, 10k steps, 0.001 LR, 3 vectors per token, using SD 1.5 base model.


Since it's not another waifu, thought I'd take the time to put this up.

modelVersions.name: v1.0
modelVersions.description:
Needs 'Man' in the prompt or it's just some rando in a suit. Also not that expressive, can't try to change that expression.

First one, so I don't know what I'm doing.
